                     <p>
                        <placeName key="place_107027">Clapcote</placeName>.
                            
                            <persName>
                           <forename>Richard</forename> 
                           <surname>Oterbourne</surname> of <placeName role="person" key="place_107027">C<supplied>lapcote</supplied>
                           </placeName>
                        </persName> grants to <persName>
                           <forename>John</forename> atte <surname>Rysshe</surname> of <persName role="person">W<supplied>allingford</supplied>
                           </persName>
                        </persName> 3 acres of arable land in <surname>C<supplied>lapcote</supplied>
                        </surname> ... viz. one acre at <placeName type="minor">le Pathe</placeName> leading to <placeName type="minor">le Westweye</placeName>, one at <placeName type="minor">le North Mulle</placeName>, and one at <placeName type="minor">Schillyng-wurthe</placeName>. Also one acre of meadow in <placeName key="place_107027">C<supplied>lapcote</supplied>
                        </placeName> ’prout sors condonat’. 
                            Witnesses: <persName>
                           <forename>Reginald</forename> le <surname>taverner</surname>
                        </persName>,
                            <persName>
                           <forename>Richard</forename> 
                           <surname>Folyot</surname>
                        </persName>,
                            <persName>
                           <forename>John</forename> 
                           <surname>Kary</surname>
                        </persName>, 
                            <persName>
                           <forename>John</forename> de <surname>Louches</surname>
                        </persName>,
                            <persName>
                           <forename>Richard</forename> atte <surname>char</surname>
                        </persName>. 
                            Given at <placeName role="date" key="place_107027">C<supplied>lapcote</supplied>
                        </placeName>.
                            <origDate when="1349-10-25">
                           <supplied>25 Oct. 1349.</supplied>
                        </origDate> 
                     </p>
